---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="PPC Management Services in Ahmedabad | Google Ads Expert | DC technolabs"
  description="Expert PPC management in Ahmedabad. Google Ads, Facebook Ads, and more. Maximize ROI with data-driven campaigns. Get immediate results!"
>
  <Header />
  <div style="height: 80px;"></div>
  
  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>PPC Management Services in Ahmedabad</h1>
      <p class="hero-subtitle">Maximize ROI with expertly managed advertising campaigns</p>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container" style="max-width: 900px;">
      <h2>Get Immediate Results with Professional PPC Management</h2>
      <p>Stop wasting money on poorly optimized ads. DC technolabs creates, manages, and optimizes Google Ads and social media campaigns that deliver measurable ROI. Based in Ahmedabad, we help businesses across Gujarat achieve their advertising goals.</p>
      
      <h3>What's Included in Our PPC Service</h3>
      <ul class="feature-list">
        <li><strong>Google Ads Campaign Setup & Management:</strong> Search, Display, Shopping, and Video ads</li>
        <li><strong>Facebook & Instagram Advertising:</strong> Targeted campaigns on social platforms</li>
        <li><strong>LinkedIn Ads:</strong> B2B advertising for professional services</li>
        <li><strong>Keyword Research & Selection:</strong> Find profitable keywords with buying intent</li>
        <li><strong>Ad Copy Creation:</strong> Compelling ads that drive clicks and conversions</li>
        <li><strong>Landing Page Optimization:</strong> Ensure your pages convert traffic</li>
        <li><strong>A/B Testing:</strong> Continuously test and improve ad performance</li>
        <li><strong>Bid Management:</strong> Optimize bids to maximize ROI</li>
        <li><strong>Conversion Tracking:</strong> Track every lead and sale accurately</li>
        <li><strong>Detailed Reporting:</strong> See exactly where your money goes and what it generates</li>
      </ul>
      
      <h3>Platforms We Manage</h3>
      <ul style="margin: 2rem 0; line-height: 2;">
        <li><strong>Google Ads:</strong> Search, Display, Shopping, YouTube</li>
        <li><strong>Facebook Ads:</strong> Facebook & Instagram campaigns</li>
        <li><strong>LinkedIn Ads:</strong> Professional B2B advertising</li>
        <li><strong>Microsoft Ads:</strong> Bing search advertising</li>
      </ul>
      
      <h3>Our PPC Process</h3>
      <ol style="margin: 2rem 0; padding-left: 1.5rem; line-height: 2;">
        <li><strong>Discovery & Goals:</strong> Understand your business and advertising objectives</li>
        <li><strong>Strategy Development:</strong> Create campaign structure and targeting plan</li>
        <li><strong>Campaign Setup:</strong> Build campaigns with optimized keywords and ads</li>
        <li><strong>Launch & Monitor:</strong> Go live and track performance closely</li>
        <li><strong>Optimize Daily:</strong> Adjust bids, pause poor performers, scale winners</li>
        <li><strong>Monthly Reporting:</strong> Review results and plan next month's strategy</li>
      </ol>
      
      <h3>Why Choose DC technolabs for PPC?</h3>
      <ul class="feature-list">
        <li><strong>Google Ads Certified:</strong> Official certification from Google</li>
        <li><strong>Data-Driven Decisions:</strong> We let numbers guide our strategy, not guesses</li>
        <li><strong>Transparent Reporting:</strong> Full access to your accounts and detailed reports</li>
        <li><strong>Proven ROI:</strong> Track record of profitable campaigns across industries</li>
        <li><strong>Continuous Optimization:</strong> We never "set and forget" your campaigns</li>
        <li><strong>Local Market Knowledge:</strong> Understanding of Ahmedabad and Gujarat audience</li>
      </ul>
      
      <h3>PPC Management Pricing</h3>
      <p><strong>Starter Package:</strong> ₹10,000/month management fee + your ad spend</p>
      <p><strong>Professional Package:</strong> ₹20,000/month management fee + your ad spend</p>
      <p><strong>Enterprise Package:</strong> Custom pricing for large budgets</p>
      <p style="font-size: 0.95rem; color: var(--text-light);">*Ad spend is paid directly to Google/Facebook. We manage it for you.</p>
      
      <h3>Common PPC Questions</h3>
      <div style="margin: 2rem 0;">
        <h4>How much should I spend on ads?</h4>
        <p>We recommend starting with ₹20,000-50,000/month in ad spend for most small businesses. This can be scaled up or down based on results.</p>
        
        <h4>How quickly will I see results?</h4>
        <p>Unlike SEO, PPC delivers immediate traffic. You'll start seeing clicks within hours of launching campaigns.</p>
        
        <h4>What's the difference between your fee and ad spend?</h4>
        <p>Our management fee covers our time and expertise. Ad spend goes directly to the platforms (Google, Facebook). Both are separate costs.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="cta-box">
        <h3>Ready to Start Getting Leads Today?</h3>
        <p>Get a free PPC audit and custom campaign strategy</p>
        <div style="display: flex; gap: 1rem; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap;">
          <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary btn-large">Get Free PPC Audit</a>
          <a href="tel:+919662608986" class="btn btn-secondary btn-large">Call +91 96626-08986</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <Footer />
</Layout>

<style>
  .page-hero {
    padding: 4rem 0 3rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--bg-dark) 0%, var(--secondary-light) 100%);
    color: white;
    text-align: center;
  }
  
  .page-hero h1 {
    color: white;
  }
  
  .hero-subtitle {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
    margin: 0;
  }
  
  .feature-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 2rem 0;
  }
  
  .feature-list li {
    padding: 1rem 0;
    padding-left: 2.5rem;
    position: relative;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-light);
  }
  
  .feature-list li::before {
    content: '✓';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--accent);
    font-weight: bold;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
  }
  
  .cta-box {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary) 0%, var(--primary-dark) 100%);
    color: white;
    padding: 3rem;
    border-radius: 1rem;
    text-align: center;
    margin: 3rem 0;
  }
  
  .cta-box h3 {
    color: white;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  
  .cta-box p {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
</style>
